title: Glenn Gould Plays Bach (13 CDs)-EAC-LAME VBR (lt)
description:
&quot;Glenn Gould plays Bach&quot; contains most of the recordings of J S Bach performed by Glenn Gould. It includes the English Suites, French Overture, French Suites, Goldberg Variations (from 1955 and 1982), Partitas, Preludes &amp; Fugues, Two- &amp; Three-Part Inventions, and the Well-Tempered Clavier Books I &amp; II.

All recordings are from my personal collection, ripped with Exact Audio Copy, and compressed with LAME.

Lazlo Toth
